{"title":"HYY迎亲II","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5463","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>HYY经历了千辛万苦，到了JCH的家，可是还有一堆困难等着他~~</p><p>（不要问我为什么这么喜欢用“~~”）</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>到了JCH的家，但一堵大铁门挡住了他，上面有一个数n，数的下面有一行奇怪的字，HYY费了九牛二虎之力才看懂，大概是：读入一个数n，用Hanoi三塔的方法求出答案S</p><p>HYY的智商不好，请你帮他算出来，让他可以进入JCH的家<span style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Grande', Helvetica, Arial, 'Microsoft YaHei', FreeSans, Arimo, 'Droid Sans', 'wenquanyi micro hei', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Hiragino Sans GB W3', FontAwesome, sans-serif;\">（此题我在洛谷上发了比赛）</span></p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个整数n</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数S</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p><p><br></p><p>1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>14</p><p><br></p><p>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>S&lt;10^200</p><p>in文件随机：</p><p>var</p><p> a:longint;</p><p>begin</p><p> randomize;</p><p> writeln(random(600)+1);</p><p>end.</p><p><br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}